name: predictor:alleleB
description: predictor 2nd allele (effect estimates are for this allele)

name: outcome:alleleB
description: outcome 2nd allele (effect estimates are for this allele)

name: missing
description: Number of samples with missing data

name: minimum_outcome_count
description: Minimum count of outcome alleleA or alleleB

name: minimum_predictor_count
description: Minimum count of predictor alleleA or alleleB

name: predictor_info
description: imputation info score for the predictor (reflecting uncertainty in imputed genotype distribution).

name: null:converged
description: Did the null model (i.e. the model with baseline and covariates but no predictor genotypes) converge? (1=yes, 0 = no)

name: null:iterations
description: How many iterations the null model took to converge

name: null:fit_time
description: How much time the null model took to converge

name: null:degrees_of_freedom
description: number of paramameters in null model

name: [name]:converged
description: Did the full model [model name] converge?

name: [name]:fit_time
description: Approximately how long the model took to fit in seconds.

name: [name]:degrees_of_freedom
description: Number of parameters in full model

name: [name]:beta_i:[parameter name]/outcome=1
description: Estimate of parameter i in full model named [name]

name: [name]:sd_i
description: Estimated posterior standard deviation for beta_i

name: [name]:cov_i,[j]
description: Estimated posterior covariance between parameters i and j

name: [name]:log10_bf
description: log10 Bayes factor for full model [model name] against the null model

name: [name]:prior_mode_i
description: Mode of the prior on parameter i (usually 0)

name: [name]:se_i
description: Approximate frequentist standard error for beta_i

name: comment
description: Comments or notifications of errors (will be NA if nothing unusual occurred).
